    <title>Adding more functionality to &cockpit;</title>
    <abstract>
      <para>
        After you deploy &cockpit; on &productname;, it
        already provides a default functionality. The following sections
        describe how to extend it by installing additional &cockpit;
        extensions. You need to reboot &productnameshort; to apply the changes.
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </info>
